    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Implement a simple trie in C++]]></title>
    <link href="http://yinyunqiao.github.io/blog/2013/09/17/implement-a-simple-trie-in-c-plus-plus/"/>
    <updated>2013-09-17T10:38:00+10:00</updated>
